<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
   <div rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="Aink216-kilavi"> varaivu nīṭa vāṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaṭkut talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat tōḻi kūṟiyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante said to the heroine, who was unable [to bear] as the marriage was delayed, while the hero was behind the hedge.    </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink216">
<l>kuṟuṅkai yirumpulik kōḷva lēṟṟai</l>
<l>neṭumputaṟ kāṉattu maṭappiṭi yīṉṟa</l>
<l>naṭuṅkunaṭaik kuḻavi koḷīiya palaviṉ</l>
<l>paḻantūṅku koḻuniḻa loḷikku nāṭaṟkuk</l>
<l>koytiṭu taḷiriṉ vāṭi niṉ</l>
<l>meypiṟi tāta levaṉkola ṉṉāy</l>
     
</lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mother, why does your body wither like a plucked sprout,  </l>
<l>and change for the man from the land where  </l>
<l rend="indent">the male of a big tiger with short paws, capable of killing,  </l>
<l rend="indent">lies hidden in the luxuriant shade of hanging jackfruit,  </l>
<l rend="indent">in order to capture the young with a trembling gait  </l>
<l rend="indent">born of a naïve female elephant in the forest with tall shrubs?</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
